using namespace std;
typedef long long int ll;
map<ll,int> mtp;
int main(){
    int tt;
    int n;
    ll x;
    cin>>n;
    mtp.clear();
    while(n--){
            cin>>x;
       ++mtp[x];
    }
    map<ll,int>::reverse_iterator it;
    int cnt = 0;
    int first = -1,second = -1;
    for(it = mtp.rbegin();it!=mtp.rend();++it){
            if(it->second==1){
                    if(first==-1)
                    first = it->first;
                    else if(second==-1)
                        second = it->first;
                        ++cnt;
            }
            else if(it->second>=2){
                    if(first==-1)
                        first = it->first;
                        if(second==-1)
                            second = it->first;
                        break;
            }
    if(cnt==2)
        break;
    }
    cout<<first<<" "<<second<<endl;
return 0;
}
